verbose_text: The MEC regimen (MEC; mitoxantrone 6 mg/m 2 on days 1-4, etoposide 80 mg/m 2 on days 1-5, and acytarabine 100 mg/m 2 on days 1-5) and gemtuzumab ozogamicin (GO 3 mg/m 2) induced third mCR.
